"cynnwys a ph'un a yw'n ddefnyddiol."

#: rh_ui/templates/info_pages/cookies.html:156
msgid ""
"In addition, if you share a link to a page, the service you share it on "
"may set a cookie. We have no\n"
"                control over cookies set on other websites – you can turn"
" them off, but not through us."
